Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.79,0:00:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.59,0:00:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  你想問什麼
